duties_responsibilities.duty: Load and unload materials by hand and with equipment, ensuring safety and efficiency in warehouse operations.
Demonstrate physical endurance and teamwork in fast-paced and physically demanding work environment.
Adhere to safety compliance protocols and handle equipment for material handling and transportation.
Maintain efficient time management to optimize productivity and contribute to rewarding production pay based on output.
Undergo pre-employment drug test and background check to ensure eligibility for warehouse employment.

education_certification.credential: High School Diploma or equivalent (18 years or older)
